summary: {{summary}}
---
section: Amendment Details
---
paragraph: This Amendment ("Amendment") is entered into as of {{amendment_date}} by and between {{provider_name}} ("Provider") and {{client_name}} ("Client") to amend that certain {{original_contract_name}} dated {{original_date}} (the "Original Agreement").
---
ref: {{original_contract_name}} | file: {{original_contract_path}} | rel: amends
ref: {{master_agreement_name}} | file: {{master_agreement_path}} | rel: governed-by
---
section: Recitals
---
paragraph: WHEREAS, the parties entered into the Original Agreement for {{original_purpose}};
paragraph: WHEREAS, the parties desire to amend certain terms and conditions of the Original Agreement as set forth herein;
paragraph: NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants contained herein, the parties agree as follows:
---
section: Amendments
---
paragraph: The following amendments are made to the Original Agreement:
---
section: General Provisions
---
paragraph: Except as expressly amended hereby, all terms and conditions of the Original Agreement remain in full force and effect.
paragraph: This Amendment may be executed in counterparts, each of which shall be deemed an original.
---
section: Approval and Execution
---
approve: Amendment reviewed by legal | by: {{legal_reviewer}} | role: Legal Counsel
